reviews.text: Nice.😁
This is only a small branch of Starbucks. Not much seating but the latte and chocolate cake were very nice!
Special coffee.
I was expelled by a staff for the most ridiculous reason : sitting too long (3hours) ... Let’s set a time limit for each table?!

Drink the drip coffee, quite okay and much more healthy than the milk drinks.  
Quite noisy to sit here, but comfortable.

reviews.text: 響V city最底層，環境比較好，因為有自然光透入。喔有室外座位，但仍然不夠。店員不會主動mark客人名，飲品製作好亦不會主動提示。杯新出既特濃焦糖咖啡凝珠星冰樂一般般，水到唔似沙冰，無想像中咁好飲，啲咖啡凝珠都唔算好重咖啡味，都係普通既焦糖咖啡好飲啲。
